'''为了保加利亚BSP'''（{{lang-bg|БСП за България}}），又称'''为了保加利亚联盟'''，是[[保加利亚|保加利亚]]的一个[[选举联盟|选举联盟]]。该联盟最早形成于1991年，后数次更名，2017年改用现名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sofiaglobe.com/2017/02/07/bulgarian-socialist-party-signs-election-coalition-deal-with-five-parties-including-communists|title=Bulgarian Socialist Party signs election coalition deal with five parties including communists|publisher=The Sofia Globe|date=2017-02-07|access-date=2017-02-08|archive-date=2017-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170228075839/http://sofiaglobe.com/2017/02/07/bulgarian-socialist-party-signs-election-coalition-deal-with-five-parties-including-communists/}}</ref>。该联盟一直由[[保加利亚社会党|保加利亚社会党]]（BSP）领导。

